snippet.title: Cynic Snacks
snippet.description:
An animated comedy channel, hosted by a talking slice of pizza, with videos focussing mainly on low-budget, bootleg movie reviews. 
Occasionally guest starring other fantastic creators such as James Marriott, Cynical Reviews, Voxis Productions, Jay Exci, Touzel and many more... 

Currently posting once a month (animation takes a while), but have lots of big things planned for the future, so stick around! 

http://www.patreon.com/cynicsnacks
http://www.instagram.com/cynicsnacks
